{"tid":536971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁愛詩母親仙遊　享壽101歲","createTime":"2018-01-22T09:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T16:47:58.000Z","uid":35519,"like":103,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c0934590e9c9a09c470b2f5ed07259eb148cb4d8","tid":536971,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:33:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梁愛詩母親仙遊<br />\n享壽101歲</span></strong><br />\n2018-01-22<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/01/22/1750382_6679571d1147972a731a7027162df78f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F1750382_6679571d1147972a731a7027162df78f.jpg&h=d8c16e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任、前律政司司長梁愛詩母親黃寶群女士，本月12日辭世，享年101歲；家人昨日在香港殯儀館設靈，今日出殯，將採火葬儀式。行政長官林鄭月娥到來弔唁，不少官商名流送花圈悼念【圖】。靈堂採素色布置，極備哀榮。"},{"pid":"78699238373a6a2462f6d699fb37cc50c7db23ac","tid":536971,"uid":8478,"like":39,"dislike":4,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"幾時到佢本人"},{"pid":"dff2444b2542aa18892dfda1d125adcdb94102e7","tid":536971,"uid":34140,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"就過年，祝佢早日母女團聚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67809ae33a115c746dad1a69a65f3c42eea24c9c","tid":536971,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8be728534b95ed174c1e90271daf03aaa316ad5","tid":536971,"uid":88689,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"睇錯梁愛詩夢遊仙境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7945ecb947be6f10b6c8dc513dc484629d1fda","tid":536971,"uid":166785,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"佢老母幾時帶埋佢走"},{"pid":"b428504ece3b87e59d929a4d6c05a59b5af0202d","tid":536971,"uid":47359,"like":23,"dislik